# Changelog

All notable changes to VIBE will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

---

## [1.0.0] - 2024-03-XX (Hackathon Release)

### Added

#### Core Features
- ✨ **Plotline Generator** - Generate AI-powered story structure and plot outlines
  - 3-act story structure generation
  - Character relationship mapping
  - Chapter breakdown suggestions
  - Markdown export

- 🔮 **Oracle Tool** - Creative brainstorming and idea generation
  - Character backstory generator
  - Plot twist suggestions
  - Dialogue examples
  - World-building assistance
  - Topic-based idea generation

- ⭐ **Judge Tool** - Automated writing feedback and evaluation
  - Plot coherence analysis
  - Character development assessment
  - Pacing evaluation
  - Tone and style feedback
  - Constructive improvement suggestions

- ✨ **Prompt Optimizer** - Refine and improve prompts for better LLM results
  - Clarity improvement
  - Context addition
  - Specificity enhancement
  - Prompt engineering guidance
  - Best practices tips

#### Infrastructure
- 🏗️ Next.js 14 full-stack application
- TypeScript for type safety
- Tailwind CSS for responsive design
- API routes for backend logic
- Support for OpenAI and Anthropic Claude APIs
- Environment variable management with .env.example

#### User Experience
- Clean, intuitive interface
- Responsive design (desktop + tablet)
- Dark/light mode ready
- Fast load times and optimized performance
- Browser-based (no installation needed)

#### Documentation
- Comprehensive README.md
- Detailed CONTRIBUTING.md guide
- CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md for community standards
- ROADMAP.md for future vision
- .gitignore for clean repository
- Inline code comments and JSDoc

#### Testing & Quality
- Basic test suite setup
- ESLint configuration
- Prettier for code formatting
- TypeScript strict mode
- Error handling foundations

